Business Card App

Overview

This project is a React frontend application that interacts with a backend API to manage business cards. Users can view business cards created by others and access relevant business information. Based on their account type, users have different functionalities available.

Features

Public Users (Non-Registered)

View all business cards created by business users.

Search for business cards and find relevant information.

Registered Users

Personal Users:

Like business cards, which will be added to a "Liked Cards" section for quick access.

Business Users:

Create new business cards.

View and manage their own created cards in the "My Cards" section.

Edit or delete their own business cards.

Like business cards from other users, similar to personal users.

Admin Users:

Edit or delete any existing business card.

Access a user CRM to manage registered users.

Edit or delete any existing user account.
